abstract: Wall Street was in suspense over SAC Capital Advisors. | Trades by Raj Rajaratnam’s younger brother may have put SAC on regulators’ radar. | Unlike the last housing boom, the buyers this time are Wall Street investors. | Turney Duff, a former stock trader, traces his descent in a new book.
